des: Fancy yourself as a bit of a kitchen DIY-er? We hear you. Now, with our new one-stop seasoning packets, you can create small-batch pickles at home the easy way. Say goodbye to expensive ingredients you'll never use again, and say hello to HomeBrew - It's as easy as produce, pint and packet. Follow along at home with Alexa as we give you some simple pickle prep guidance, and set you on your way to pickle mastery!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
